,"removed":true,"required":false,"displayName":"CV / Resume Upload  ","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Anything you want us to know? (optional)  ","type":"string","display":true,"removed":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Anything you want us to know? (optional)  ","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"score","type":"string","display":true,"removed":true,"required":false,"displayName":"score","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"seniority","type":"string","display":true,"removed":true,"required":false,"displayName":"seniority","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"recommendation","type":"string","display":true,"removed":true,"required":false,"displayName":"recommendation","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"matched_skills","type":"string","display":true,"removed":true,"required":false,"displayName":"matched_skills","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"missing_skills","type":"string","display":true,"removed":true,"required":false,"displayName":"missing_skills","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"nice_to_have_matched","type":"string","display":true,"removed":true,"required":false,"displayName":"nice_to_have_matched","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"experience_comment","type":"string","display":true,"removed":true,"required":false,"displayName":"experience_comment","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"red_flags","type":"string","display":true,"removed":true,"required":false,"displayName":"red_flags","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"summary","type":"string","display":true,"removed":true,"required":false,"displayName":"summary","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"HR_Decision","type":"string","display":true,"removed":true,"required":false,"displayName":"HR_Decision","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Email_Status","type":"string","display":true,"removed":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Email_Status","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"Interview_Time","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"Interview_Time","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"row_number","type":"number","display":true,"removed":true,"readOnly":true,"required":false,"displayName":"row_number","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true}],"mappingMode":"defineBelow","matchingColumns":["Email Address"],"attemptToConvertTypes":false,"convertFieldsToString":false},"options":{},"operation":"update","sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":358702502,"cachedResultUrl":"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1NBsshSSl7LVfn-TnP8JyhcoLTl7g0YTsvrpMZygN670/edit#gid=358702502","cachedResultName":"Form Responses 1"},"documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"1NBsshSSl7LVfn-TnP8JyhcoLTl7g0YTsvrpMZygN670","cachedResultUrl":"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1NBsshSSl7LVfn-TnP8JyhcoLTl7g0YTsvrpMZygN670/edit?usp=drivesdk","cachedResultName":"Athena Jobs"}},"credentials":{"googleSheetsOAuth2Api":{"id":"pqhCUJdTO98td28J","name":"Google Sheets account"}},"typeVersion":4.7},{"id":"ef677918-8c1d-4925-b343-485575ab1ba7","name":"Sticky Note12","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[432,1296],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":416,"height":320,"content":"## 📅 Calendly Event Listener\n\nListens for two Calendly events in real time:\n- invitee.created — candidate booked an interview\n- invitee.canceled — candidate canceled\n\nRoutes each event to the correct branch for handling.\n\n"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"35590ea8-1984-4322-b7ed-de405fd4f0de","name":"Sticky Note13","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[880,960],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":640,"height":368,"content":"## ✅ Interview Booked\n\nWhen a candidate books an interview, the start time \nis extracted from the Calendly payload, formatted \nto your local timezone, and written to the \nInterview_Time column in the sheet — matched by \nthe candidate's email address.\n\n→ Change the timezone format in the Date & Time \n  node to match your region."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"c3dc373a-b640-4569-8dea-30dc28bcdfc1","name":"Sticky Note14","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[880,1344],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":640,"height":368,"content":"## ❌ Cancellation Handler\n\nWhen a candidate cancels, the IF node checks if \nthis is a true cancellation or a reschedule. If \nrescheduled (rescheduled = true), the workflow \nstops — the new booking event handles the update \nautomatically. If genuinely canceled, \"Meeting \ncanceled\" is written to the Interview_Time column."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"51931afa-9265-4d97-9833-30e9012e2513","name":"Sticky Note15","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[336,944],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":1344,"height":800,"content":"\n\n# #3 Calendly Interview Tracker"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"fb90c285-bfc9-4a85-8100-d16d10175b4b","name":"Sticky Note16","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-1792,-464],"parameters":{"width":592,"height":2384,"content":"## 🏢 AI CV Screening & Interview Pipeline for Agencies\n\n**Built for agencies hiring across multiple roles.**  \nA candidate fills a Google Form → AI scores their CV → \nHR decides in a sheet → email sends automatically → \nCalendly tracks the interview. Fully connected. Zero manual steps.\n\n---\n\n### 👤 Who Is This For?\nDigital agencies and hiring teams managing applications \nfor multiple job roles simultaneously. Works out of the \nbox for: n8n Automation Developer, React Developer, \nSEO Expert, Meta Ads Expert. Swap in any roles you need.\n\n---\n\n### ⚙️ How It Works\n\n**WORKFLOW 1 — CV Screening Pipeline**\n\n1. Triggers every minute when a new Google Form \n   response row is added to the sheet\n2. Extracts the Google Drive file ID from the CV \n   upload URL (handles all 3 Drive URL formats)\n3. Checks n8n Data Table — if email already exists, \n   workflow stops (duplicate protection)\n4. New email is logged to the Data Table immediately\n5. Routes candidate to the correct job profile based \n   on the role they selected in the form\n6. Each job profile defines: required skills, \n   nice-to-have skills, minimum years, seniority \n   thresholds (Junior/Mid/Senior), and scoring \n   weights (technical/experience/nice-to-have)\n7. All branches merge into one clean data object \n   with standardized field names\n8. CV is downloaded from Google Drive using the \n   extracted file ID\n9. PDF is converted to plain text\n10. AI evaluates the CV against the job profile using \n    a dynamically built prompt — scoring is weighted \n    per role, not generic\n11. Returns structured JSON: score, seniority, \n    recommendation, matched skills, missing skills, \n    nice-to-have matched, red flags, summary\n12. All results written back to the same Google \n    Sheet row, matched by email address\n\n**WORKFLOW 2 — HR Decision Email Sender**\n\n13. Watches the sheet every minute for changes to \n    the HR_Decision column\n14. IF node checks: HR_Decision is filled AND \n    Email_Status is not already \"Sent\" (prevents \n    duplicate emails)\n15. HR types exactly \"Send Invite\" or \n    \"Send Rejection\" in the HR_Decision column\n16. Switch routes to the correct email template\n17. Invite email includes a pre-filled Calendly \n    link with candidate name and email\n18. Rejection email sends a respectful, \n    encouraging message\n19. Gmail sends the email\n20. Email_Status column is updated to \"Sent\" \n    immediately after sending\n\n**WORKFLOW 3 — Calendly Interview Tracker**\n\n21. Listens for Calendly events in real time: \n    invitee.created and invitee.canceled\n22. Routes by event type\n23. Booking: extracts start time, formats to \n    local timezone, writes to Interview_Time column\n24. Cancellation: checks if this is a real \n    cancellation or a reschedule — if rescheduled, \n    stops (the new booking event handles it); \n    if genuinely canceled, writes \"Meeting canceled\"\n\n---\n\n### 🛠️ Setup Steps\n\n- [ ] Connect Google Sheets Trigger credential  \n      (use OAuth2, point to your Form Responses sheet)\n- [ ] Connect Google Drive credential  \n      (needs read access to the Drive folder where  \n      Google Form uploads CVs)\n- [ ] Connect OpenRouter credential  \n      (get free API key at openrouter.ai — free models  \n      available for testing)\n- [ ] Connect Gmail credential (OAuth2)\n- [ ] Connect Calendly credential (OAuth2)\n- [ ] In **Invitation Message** node → replace  \n      YOUR_CALENDLY_LINK with your actual Calendly URL\n- [ ] Add these columns to your Google Sheet manually:  \n      score | seniority | recommendation |  \n      matched_skills | missing_skills |  \n      nice_to_have_matched | experience_comment |  \n      red_flags | summary | HR_Decision |  \n      Email_Status | Interview_Time\n- [ ] Create an n8n Data Table named \"CV Screening\"  \n      with one column: Email (string)\n- [ ] Customize each Job Profile Set node with your  \n      agency's actual role requirements and skill lists\n\n---\n\n### 🎨 Customization\n\n**To add a new job role:**\n1. Add a new option to your Google Form dropdown\n2. Add a new condition to the Route by Job Role \n   Switch node\n3. Duplicate any Job Profile Set node and update \n   the skill fields for the new role\n\n\n**To change scoring weights:**\nOpen the relevant Job Profile Set node and update \ntech_weight, experience_weight, nice_to_have_weight. \nThey must add up to 100.\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ Important Notes\n\n- HR_Decision column values are case-sensitive:  \n  type **Send Invite** or **Send Rejection** exactly\n- The Calendly booking email must match the  \n  candidate's application email for Interview_Time  \n  to update correctly (the invite link pre-fills  \n  this automatically)\n- This template contains 3 separate workflows —  \n  all 3 must be active for the full pipeline to work"},"typeVersion":1}],"pinData":{},"connections":{"If":{"main":[[{"node":"Switch","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Switch":{"main":[[{"node":"Invitation Message","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Rejection Message","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Job Profile":{"main":[[{"node":"Normalize Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Job Profile1":{"main":[[{"node":"Normalize Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Job Profile2":{"main":[[{"node":"Normalize Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Job Profile3":{"main":[[{"node":"Normalize Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Normalize Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Download CV from Drive","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Extract CV Text":{"main":[[{"node":"Evaluate Candidate","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Is Email Unique?":{"main":[[{"node":"Add Email to Table","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Mark as Canceled":{"main":[[{"node":"Log Cancellation","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Rejection Message":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Rejection Email","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Job Role":{"main":[[{"node":"Job Profile","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Job Profile1","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Job Profile2","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Job Profile3","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Add Email to Table":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Job Role","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Evaluate Candidate":{"main":[[{"node":"Update in Sheet","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Extract CV File ID":{"main":[[{"node":"Is Email Unique?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Invitation Message":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Interview Invite","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Event Type":{"main":[[{"node":"Extract Booking Details","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Skip if Rescheduled","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Skip if Rescheduled":{"main":[[{"node":"Mark as Canceled","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Rejection Email":{"main":[[{"node":"Mark Invite Sent1","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Format Interview Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Log Interview Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Google Sheets Trigger":{"main":[[{"node":"If","type":"main","index":0}]]},"OpenRouter Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Evaluate Candidate","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Send Interview Invite":{"main":[[{"node":"Mark Invite Sent","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Download CV from Drive":{"main":[[{"node":"Extract CV Text","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Extract Booking Details":{"main":[[{"node":"Format Interview Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Interview Event Received":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Event Type","type":"main","index":0}]]},"New Application Received":{"main":[[{"node":"Extract CV File ID","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Structured Output Parser":{"ai_outputParser":[[{"node":"Evaluate Candidate","type":"ai_outputParser","index":0}]]}}}